question: PTID
conformity: String with max length of 10 characters
notes: Follow your Center's Patient ID scheme; use same ID as in MDS, if subject is enrolled in MDS.

question: ADRC name
notes: Use your Center ID. Valid codes are available here: https://naccdata.org/center-ids

question: ADRC Visit Number
notes: Can be determined by Center. The Center may use its existing visit number scheme. It is not required to start with 1.
